##-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------#
Subprog MAJ
#** Called from  DOSMAJ90
#*!
#-- MAJ CACCEDEF to take into account the move of the value "None" from 26 to 34 in the local menu 693
Call UTI_MOUL([F:ADS]DOSSIER) From UTICPT90 #*YYFIN-X3-30158 : Migration of default dimensions (CACCEDEF table)

# Issue X3-59287 - 2017-11-08 by FHA : ST1 ST2 ST3 records replicated in GDD as STT1 STT2 STT3
Call UTI_MOUL([F:ADS]DOSSIER) From UTICPT94

# Issue X3-52049 - 2018-01-22 by FHA : ORI ORIC records initiated in GDD if necessary
Call UTI_MOUL([F:ADS]DOSSIER) From UTICPT95

# Issue X3-52049 - 2018-01-24 by BEFOU : Origin of G/L entry - Migration
Call UTI_MOUL([F:ADS]DOSSIER) From UTICPT96

Call UTI_MOUL([F:ADS]DOSSIER) From UTICPT97 # Issue X3-83028 - 2018-05-18 by CBO : Add a parameter to modify or not purchase order

Call UTI_MOUL([F:ADS]DOSSIER) From UTIFIN002 # Issue X3-111845 - 2018-10-16 by CBO : New acc task

Call UTI_MOUL([F:ADS]DOSSIER) From UTIBOX201808001 # Issue X3-113123 - 2018-10-19 by CATUA : 1099-DIV box definition data values for 2018

End
